														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2731898">
									

<p>The whole conceit of Omega-7 in this series taking on SCP-2000 reminds me of the entire concept of <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Riverdale_(2017_TV_series)">Riverdale</a>: trying to integrate characters and concepts from bygone eras into a more modern setting, but coming off silly and even more irrelevant as a result.</p>
<p>In short, my response to this is the same it has been to the entirety of Resurrection:</p>
<p>&quot;No. Just&#8230; no.&quot;</p>

